text.0: Biafra Today shared 10 photographs and claimed that every one pictured were civilian victims of killings and violence in Obigbo, a community in Rivers State. However, investigations show something different. Read the fact-check here: https://t.co/eVaqGcBWwF #DubawaChecks
text.1: Many cultures believe thunderstorms are sent to destroy people, animal and things because of the destruction they often leave in their wake but is this the truth? Read the facts here: https://t.co/Ke9goPYhLf #DubawaChecks
text.2: Is it true that the recipients of the 3.18 billion naira fund from the Federal Government for Micro, Small and Medium Enterprise (MSME) do not exist? Read the facts here: https://t.co/0tVvsKHkOy #DubawaChecks
